{{Infobox magazine | title = Where Magazine | image_file = <!-- cover.jpg (omit the "file: prefix --> | image_size = <!-- 220px (the default if no size is stated) --> | image_alt = | image_caption = | editor = | editor_title = | previous_editor = | staff_writer = | photographer = | category = [[Tourism]] | frequency = monthly | circulation = 2,186,284 | publisher = | founder = | founded = 1938 | firstdate = <!-- {{Start date|year|month|day}} --> | company = *[[Asia City Media Group]] ([[Asia]]) *[http://www.wheretraveler.com/classic/index.html Morris Visitor Publications] (global) *[[St. Joseph Media]] ([[Canada]]) | country = Multiple (see prose) | based = [[Toronto]], [[Ontario]], [[Canada]], Augusta, Ga US | language = <!--at september 2011, left blank. unclear at moment if all are in english or some in local language--> | website = [http://www.where.ca where.ca], ''Where Canada'' [http://www.wheretraveler.com/ wheretraveler.com] }}
'''''Where''''' is a series of magazines for tourists, distributed at hotels, convention centres, regional malls and other tourist areas.
==History== The original edition was founded in 1938.
==Publishers== Throughout most of the world, the magazine's editions are published by [http://www.wheretraveler.com Morris Visitor Publications]; it is published in Milan (Italy) by [[Where Italia Srl]], in Rome by Tourist Media Srl, in Canada by [[St. Joseph Media]] and in Asia by [[Asia City Media Group]].
